snippet.title: The Forest - Announcement Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
The Forest is an exciting, beautiful and terrifying survival horror game from Developer Endnight Games. As the lone survivor of a passenger jet crash, you find yourself in a mysterious forest battling to stay alive against a society of cannibalistic mutants. 
Build, explore and survive survive in this terrifying first person survival horror simulator.

Visit http://survivetheforest.com/ for more information

Follow developer Endnight at https://twitter.com/endnightgame
